ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of October, 1984, the Court assumes plenary jurisdiction of the above-captioned matter pursuant to 42 Pa.C.S. § 726 and ORDERS as follows:
The motion to transfer the within appeals to the Commonwealth Court is denied.
The Order of the Court of Common Pleas of Delaware County dated August 29, 1984, entered at Nos. 84-4885, 84-4969 and 84-5968, is affirmed.
